data.title: Need for consistent beach lifeguard data collection: results from an international survey
data.meta_description: Inconsistencies in lifeguard data collection present challenges to operations, safety education and prevention efforts, research and policy relying on these data. Variation in definitions, methods and collected variables generally restricts analysis to a single BLSP with limited generalisability to …
